    select * 
    from {{home}}.thrive_cex 
)
select
toDate(date_trunc('month', toDateTime(f.block_timestamp_minute))) as transaction_month,
to_cex.exchange as to_cex,
from_cex.exchange from_cex,
sum(f.eth) as eth,
sum(f.eth*eth_usd.price_close) as usd

from {{home}}.flows as f left join
cex as to_cex on f.to_address = to_cex.address left join
cex as from_cex on f.from_address = from_cex.address left join
prices.eth_usd as eth_usd on f.block_timestamp_minute = eth_usd.timestamp
